Ko da hukumomin leƙen asirinmu sun kasance mafi kyau a duniya, to ba da ikon yin tambayoyin dole ga kowa game da bayanin da "ke nuna alaƙar tattalin arziƙin Ostiraliya da wata ƙasa," ko ayyukan da ke "kawo matsala ga ra’ayin Ostiraliya " ya wuce iyaka.
