An kona Kotu a lokacin zanga-zanga a California
Oakland, Ca.-Masu zanga-zanga a Kalifoniya sun cinna wuta a wata kotu, sun lalata wani ofishin "yan sanda tare da cin zarafin jami'ai bayan wata zanga-zangar lumana ta kara karfi a yammacin Asabar", in ji "yan sandan akland.
Masu zanga-zangar sun fasa tagogi, sun fesa rubutu a jikin zane, sun yi harbi da tartsatsin wuta da kuma nuna wuta a kan jami'an, in ji sashen na Oakland a shafin Twitter.
Tweets da yawa sun yi kira ga zaman lafiya kuma sun nemi masu shirya "don taimaka mana samar da wurare masu aminci da wuraren tsaro ga masu zanga-zangar".
Zanga-zangar ta fara ne da yammacin ranar Asabar tare da ƙungiyoyi irin su "Wall of Moms," kwatankwacin ƙungiyar da aka kafa a Portland, Oregon; a yayin da masu zanga-zangar ke fuskantar wakilan Amurka da aka tura zuwa wannan garin don tsaron kotun tarayya.
Shugaba Donald Trump ya tura wakilai na tarayya don kashe wutar zanga-zangar da ke faruwa a dare tun daga mutuwar George Floyd a Minneapolis a ranar 25 ga Mayu.
Zanga-zangar a Oakland ta fara cikin lumana, amma daga baya ta rikide ta zama ta dare.
"Yan sanda sun ayyana" haramtacciyar taro "da misalin karfe 11: 30 na dare. Kuma jami'ai sun nemi taron jama'a su watse.
Gobarar ta tashi ne a Babban Kotun Koli na Alameda kuma an dauke ta cikin kankanin lokaci daga baya, kafafen yada labarai sun ruwaito.
'Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar a wani lokaci "suna fasa tagogi suna rera wakokin nuna wariyar launin fata ga mazauna yankin".
Hotuna tweeted da sashen nuna karya gilashi da kuma Paint splattered a wani dan sanda gini.
An Samu Tsaron Tsaro a Wajen Ofishin Jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu, China
Akwai tsauraran matakan tsaro a wajen karamin ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke birnin Chengdu na kasar Sin a ranar Lahadi, yayin da ma'aikatan Amurkan ke shirin barin harabar.
An ga manyan motoci guda uku masu motsi suna shiga harabar ginin, yayin da "yan sanda sanye da kayan farin kaya suka yi layi duka bangarorin titin, wadanda aka yi musu shinge da karfe.
Editan jaridar ta Times ta China ya wallafa a shafinsa na Tweeter cewa an bai wa karamin ofishin jakadancin Amurka da ke Chengdu awanni 72 ya rufe, ko kuma har zuwa karfe 10 na safe (0200GMT) Litinin, 27 ga Yuli.
China ta tuhumi cewa wasu ma'aikata a karamin ofishin jakadancin Chengdu suna "gudanar da ayyukan da ba su dace da asalinsu ba".
Ba tare da bayar da wani bayani ba, kakakin Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Cana, Wang Wenbin ya ce irin wannan aiki ya zama tsoma baki cikin harkokin ƙasar Cana kuma ya cutar da muradunta na tsaro.
Umarnin da Cana ta bayar na rufe ƙaramin ofishin jakadanci a Chengdu ya fito ne a ranar Juma’a a matsayin ramuwar gayya ga umarnin da Amurka ta bayar na rufe ƙaramin ofishin jakadancin Canada ke Houston, Texas.
Washington ta umarci China da ta rufe ofishin Houston "don kare hikimar Amurkawa da bayanan sirri na Amurkawa".
Yayin da rufe karamin ofishin jakadancin China a Houston ya fara aiki a ranar Juma'a, an ga wasu gungun maza wadanda suka bayyana su jami'an Amurka ne suna kutsawa cikin ginin ta kofar baya.
Wang ya ce a ranar Asabar din da ta keta yarjejeniyar kasa da kasa da bangarorin biyu kuma China za ta mayar da martani, ba tare da bayyana yadda za ta yi ba.
Rufe titin-da-tat ya kara dagula rikice-rikicen da ke tsakanin kasashen biyu kan batutuwan da suka shafi kasuwanci da leken asirin masana'antu zuwa hakkin dan adam.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta ce dubban masu adawa da Pakistan a Afghanistan
ISLAMABAD - Wani rahoton Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya ya ce sama da ‘yan tawayen Pakistan 6,000 ke ɓoye a Afghanistan, mafi yawansu na haramtacciyar ƙungiyar Taliban ce ta Pakistan da ke da alhakin kai hari kan sojojin Pakistan da kuma fararen hula.
Rahoton da aka fitar a wannan makon ya ce ƙungiyar, wadda aka fi sani da Tehreek-e-Taliban (TTP), ta haɗe da wani reshen Afghanistan da ke ƙungiyar IS.
Wasu daga cikin membobin TTP har sun shiga ƙungiyar ta IS, wadda ke da hedikwata a gabashin Afghanistan.
Gwamnatin Afghanistan ba ta ba da amsa ba a ranar Lahadi ga buƙatun da Kamfanin Dillancin Labaran Associated ya yi don yin sharhi.
Rahoton ya ce, IS a Afghanistan da aka fi sani da IS a lardin Khorasan, ta sha da ƙyar daga jami’an tsaron Afghanistan da na Amurka da na NATO, har ma a wasu lokutan daga ƙungiyar Taliban ta Afghanistan.
Rahoton ya fito ne daga kwamitin  bincike da sanya takunkumi na Majalisar Ɗinkin Duniya, wadda ke bin diddigin ƙungiyoyin 'yan ta'adda a duniya.
Rahoton ya ƙiyasta mambobin ƙungiyar ta IS a Afghanistan da 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabancinta ya ƙare, har yanzu ƙungiyar ta IS ana sanya ta cikin shugabanninƙasar Syria Abu Said Mohammad al-Khorasani.
Rahoton ya kuma ce tawagar masu sa idon ta samu labarin cewa, wasu manyan kwamandojin ƙungiyar ta Daular Islama, Abu Qutaibah da Abu Hajar al-Iraqi, ba da jimawa ba suka isa Afghanistan daga Gabas ta Tsakiya.
"Kodayake a cikin ta ja da baya, (Daular musulinci) tana iya aiwatar da manyan hare-hare a sassa daban-daban na ƙasar, ciki har da Kabul.
Yana nufin jawo hankalin mayaƙan Taliban da ke adawa da yin yarjejeniya da Amurka, "in ji rahoton, tana magana kan yarjejeniyar zaman lafiyar Amurka da aka sanya wa hannu tare da Taliban a watan Fabrairu.
An ƙulla wannan yarjejeniyar ne don ba wa Amurka damar kawo ƙarshen shiga tsakani na shekaru 19 a Afghanistan, kuma ta yi kira ga Taliban da ta tabbatar da cewa ƙungiyoyin ‘yan ta’adda ba za su yi amfani da yankin nata ba.
Haka kuma ana sa ran yarjejeniyar za ta ba wa ƙungiyar Taliban tabbaci na shiga cikin yaƙi da ƙungiyar IS.
Na biyu kuma wataƙila mafi mahimmanci a yarjejeniyar ya buƙaci tattaunawa tsakanin Taliban da shugabancin siyasar Kabul.
Da yammacin ranar Asabar, Ma'aikatar Harkokin Wajen Amurka ta ba da wata sanarwa tana cewa, wakilinta na zaman lafiya Zalmay Khalilzad ya sake kutsawa cikin yankin yana neman sake fara wannan tattaunawa, wadda aka maimaita jinkirta yin ta yayin da ɓangarorin biyu ke taƙaddama kan shirin sakin fursuna.
Yarjejeniyar da Amurka ke mara wa baya ta buƙaci gwamnatin Afghanistan da ta saki fursunoni ‘yan Taliban 5,000, sannan kuma ‘yan Taliban ɗin su saki jami’an gwamnati da sojoji 1,000 a matsayin abin da ake kira kyakkyawar alama da za ta nuna sakamakon tattaunawa mai kyau.
