Babban bankin Burtaniya HSBC ya musanta "kafa tarko" ga Huawei na Cana a binciken Amurka - Labarin Kasuwanci na RT
Babban bankin HSBC mai hedikwata a Landan ya shiga shafukan sada zumunta domin cewa, ba haka ba ne kamar yadda kafofin yaɗa labaran Cana suka ce, "shedun ƙarya" a kan Huawei, wanda ya kai ga kame babbar jami’ar kuɗi ta kamfanin a Kanada.
A wani saƙon da ba a samu yanzu ba a WeChat, mai ba da lamunin ta ce ayyukan da ta yi ba su haifar da binciken Amurka ba a kan babban kamfanin da ke samar da kayayyakin sadarwa a duniya ba, kamar yadda binciken kamfanin Huawei ke zargin karya takunkumin da Amurka ta sanya wa Iran ya fara tun kafin shigar bankin a ƙarshen 2016.
"HSBC ba ya da wata ƙiyayya ga Huawei kuma bai yi wa  "Huawei” “tarko” ba," in ji bankin a ranar Asabar, yana mai ƙara da cewa, ba zai taɓa gurɓata wata hujja game da abokan hulɗarsa ba.
"Dangane da bukatar US DOJ [Ma'aikatar Shari'a ta Amurka] don neman bayani, HSBC Group kawai ta gabatar da gaskiyar manufar.
HSBC ba ta "kirkirar" shaida ko "boye" hujjojin ba. "
Hakanan akan rt.com yunƙurin UK na hana Huawei daga hanyar sadarwa na 5G ya nuna Amurka tana faɗan manufofin ƙetare na Biritaniya - George Galloway zuwa bunkasawa
An toshe sakon a dandamali tare da bayanin cewa "ya saba ka'idoji" kuma babu shi yanzu.
Wannan bayanin ya zo ne jim kadan bayan kafofin watsa labarai da yawa na kasar Sin, ciki har da jaridun da ke da nasaba da gwamnati, suka zargi HSBC da "kulla" alaka da Washington don shirya wa Huawei tarko.
Kamfanin ya kasance a tsakiyar badaƙalar difilomasiyya fiye da shekara da rabi tun lokacin da aka kama babbar jami’ar kuɗi ta Huawei CFO Meng Wanzhou a watan Disambar 2018 a Kanada bisa sammacin Amurka.
Meng na fuskantar tuhumar zamba kan zargin yin amfani da rigar kamfanin don karya takunkumin da aka sanya wa Iran da kuma zargin yin ƙarya ga bankuna game da alaƙar da ke tsakanin Huawei da kamfanin Iran na Skycom.
A sabuwar shaidar da Global Times ta ambata, HSBC na sane da alaƙar kamfanin Cana da Skycom.
Bankin ya bayar da rahoton cewa, ya zaɓi "haɗa baki" da gwamnatin Amurka don guje wa hukunci mai tsanani a shekarar 2012, lokacin da bankin ya amince da shigar da kuɗaɗen haram da karya takunkumi, gami da takura wa Iran.
An umarce shi a lokacin da ya biya kusan dala biliyan 1.9 a matsayin kuɗin fansa kuma don hana kowace irin ɗabi'a maras kyau irinta.
"Shaidun sun nuna cewa, HSBC ya fahimci wannan dangantakar amma da gangan ya sayar da bayanan sirrin abokan cinikinsa ga ɓangaren Amurka don gwamnatin Amurka ta iya yin watsi da rashin ɗa'a da bankin na Burtaniya ya yi, ba tare da ladabtar da ita ba a ƙarƙashin Yarjejeniyar da aka Ƙaddamar da Laifuka na 2012," in ji jaridar a cikin ɗaya daga cikin labaranta game da lamarin.
A cikin gargaɗin da ta rufe, jaridar da ke da iko a Beijing ta ƙara da cewa, mai bayar da bashin, idan har aka tabbatar da laifin wannan "haɗin bakin," zai iya fuskantar "hukunci mai tsanani" a Cana, ɗaya daga cikin manyan kasuwannin HSBC.
Ba wannan ne karo na farko da shahararren bankin ya sha suka a makonnin da suka gabata ba.
A watan da ya gabata, HSBC ta kasance cikin ladabi saboda tallafa wa sabuwar dokar tsaron ƙasa ga Hong Kong, garin da kasuwancinsa ya fara kuma wanda ke ɗauke da fiye da rabin ribarsa.
Bankin ya fuskanci suka daga ɓangarorin biyu - daga Yammacin duniya, inda Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya kira amincewar a matsayin "haɗin kan kowtow," sannan aGabas, in da rahotanni suka ce ɓangaren na Cana na cewa goyon bayan nasa "ya yi jinkiri."
