SEATTLE - Bayan makonni da aka kwashe ana gumurzu tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da hukumomin tarayya a Portland, Ore., dandazon jama’a kimanin 2,000 sun yi taro a Seattle a ranar Asabar, suna tafe a kan tituna suna arangama da ‘yan sanda.
