Wasu sun fasa tagogin wuraren kasuwancin da ke kusa.
‘Yan sanda sun yi fito-na-fito da jama’a a Capitol Hill, inda suka baza gurneti da barkonon tsohuwa kafin su fara kama mutane suna tsarewa.
Bipasha Mukherjee, 52, daga Kirkland, Wash., Ta ce ta yi zanga-zanga a kan tituna tun watan Mayu kuma ta ce akwai matuƙar damuwa a gare ta ganin irin wannan dabarun 'yan sanda.
"Wannan ba ƙasar da na yi hijira ba ce," in ji Madam Mukherjee, wadda  ta zo daga Indiya sama da shekaru 30 da suka gabata.
"Ina ji kamar muna hanzarin zama jihar masu ra'ayin kama-karya da kuma jihar 'yan sanda."
Michaud Savage na Seattle ya ce zanga-zangar an yi ta ne ga hukumomin yankin da kuma tura jami’an gwamnatin tarayya da suka yi wata zanga-zangar adawa da zanga-zangar da aka daɗe ana yi a Portland.
