Bayan Shugaba Trump ya ba da umarnin zartarwa don kare mutum-mutumi da dukiyar tarayya, Ma'aikatar Tsaron Cikin Gida ta tura tawagogin dabaru zuwa cikin gari, inda aka fara jerin rikice-rikicen da ya haifar da jikkata masu zanga-zangar, binciken sufeto-janar da kira daga shugabannin yankin ga wakilan tarayya da su tafi.
