Shivraj Singh Chouhan Akan Gwada Ingantaccen Sahihi
Babban Ministan Madhya Pradesh Shivraj Singh Chouhan, wanda a ranar Asabar ya tabbatar da cewa ya yi gwajin cutar ta COVID-19, a shafinsa na Tweeter ranar Lahadi da safe cewa yana "lafiya" kuma ya ba da yabo ga ma'aikatan gaba-gaba a yakin da ake yi da cutar ta coronavirus.
Babban Ministan ya kuma maimaita gargadin nasa daga jiya, lokacin da ya bukaci mutane da su bi ka'idoji, kamar nisantar da jama'a da amfani da abin rufe fuska.
"Ina cikin koshin lafiya, abokaina. Sadaukarwar mayaƙan coronavirus, waɗanda suka sadaukar da rayukansu, abin a yaba ne. Ina jinjina wa dukkan mayaƙan coronavirus na jihar", Mista Chouhan ya wallafa a shafinsa na Tweita daga asibitin Chirayu na Bhopal, inda aka kwantar da shi a jiya.
"Kiyaye nisan mita biyu, wanke hannuwanku akai-akai kuma sanya takunkumin rufe fuska-wadannan su ne manyan makamai da muke da su don kauce wa coronavirus. Ina kira ga dukkan mutane-ku yi amfani da wadannan makamai don kanku da masoyanku", in ji shi.
Mr Chouhan ya kara da cewa "Dukkanku ku yi hankali, ku zauna lafiya da koshin lafiya. Wannan ita ce addu'ar da nake yi wa Allah".
A ranar Asabar Mr Chouhan ya wallafa a shafinsa na Tweeter cewa ya yi gwajin kwayar cutar duk da kokarin da ya yi na kauce wa kamuwa da cutar kuma ya yi gargadin cewa "dan rashin kulawa ne kawai ke gayyatar coronavirus".
A sakon da ya wallafa a safiyar yau Mr Chouhan ya ce duk da barazanar kamuwa da cutar "babu bukatar a ji tsoro" ya kuma bukaci wadanda ke nuna alamun da su gwada kansu.
"Idan kun kamu da cutar, to babu bukatar ku ji tsoro. Kada ku ɓoye alamun cutar amma ku gaya wa likitoci nan da nan, don haka za a iya fara jinya. Kulawa da kan lokaci zai ba ku lafiya", in ji shi.
Madhya Pradesh tana da cutar kusan 27,000 COVID-19, wanda sama da 7,600 ke aiki kuma 799 sun mutu masu nasaba da kwayar.
Indiya ta sami karuwar karuwa a cikin wadanda suka kamu da COVID-19 a cikin makonnin da suka gabata, tare da gano sabbin kamuwa 45,000 a kowace rana tun daga ranar 23 ga Yuli.
Adadin adadin wadanda aka tabbatar sun kamu da cutar coronavirus yana da hanzari zuwa 14 lakh; daga cikin wadannan fiye da 4.67 lakh suna aiki ne kuma sama da 32,000 suna da nasaba da kwayar cutar.
Karuwar da aka samu a lokuta, yayi dai-dai da annashuwa game da ragowar jagororin kulle-kulle a yankunan da ba a kayyade kasar, ya sanya Indiya ta zama ta uku a jerin kasashen da abin ya shafa.
Amurka kawai (batutuwa lakh 41,78) da Brazil (23.94 lakh lokuta) sun fi muni.
Ministan cikin gida na Tunisia ya nada sabon PM, domin kafa gwamnati cikin wata guda
An nada Ministan cikin gida na Tunisia Hichem Mechichi don kafa gwamnati mai zuwa, in ji ofishin shugaban kasar, a yayin da rikicin siyasa tsakanin manyan jam'iyyu a kasar ta Arewacin Afirka.
Lauyan mai shekaru 46 ya gaji Elyes Fakhfakh, wanda ya yi murabus daga mukamin Firayim Minista a farkon wannan watan.
Amma Mechichi ba ya daga cikin sunayen da jam'iyyun siyasa masu mulki suka gabatar wa Shugaba Kais Saied.
A wata sanarwa da ya biyo bayan sanarwar ta ranar Asabar, Mechichi ya ce zai "yi aiki don kafa gwamnatin da za ta cimma burin dukkan 'yan Tunusiya".
An yaba wa Tunisia a matsayin labarin nasarar da ba kasafai ake samu ba ga canjin dimokuradiyya bayan boren kasashen Larabawa na yankin wanda ya haifar da juyin juya halin shekarar 2011.
Amma shugabannin sun sha wahala don biyan bukatun mutanen Tunisia kuma tattalin arzikin da tuni ya tabarbare ya sha fama da rufe iyakokin kasar saboda annobar COVID-19.
Cutar ta kashe kusan mutane 50 kuma ta kamu da fiye da 1,400 a Tunisia.
Kazalika kasancewa ministan cikin gida a cikin gwamnati mai fita, Mechichi ya kasance mai ba da shawara ga Shugaba Saied, yana kula da al'amura na shari'a.
Ya taba zama shugaban ma'aikata a Ma'aikatar Sufuri sannan kuma ya yi aiki a Ma'aikatar Harkokin Jama'a.
Yanzu yana da wata guda don kafa gwamnati, wanda daga nan zai fuskanci kuri'ar amincewa da majalisar dokoki kuma zai bukaci cikakken rinjaye don yin nasara.
Idan ba haka ba, za a rusa majalisar kuma za a gudanar da sabon zabe cikin watanni uku.
A zabukan karshe da aka gudanar a watan Oktoba, jam'iyyar Ennahdha ce ta hau kan karagar mulki amma ta kasa samun mafi yawa kuma daga karshe ta amince ta shiga cikin gwamnatin hadaka.
Murabus din Fakhfakh a ranar 15 ga watan Yulin, bayan kasa da watanni biyar kan karagar mulki, ya yi barazanar haifar da sabuwar baraka ta siyasa a kasar yayin da take fama da tabarbarewar tattalin arziki na annobar.
Murabus din ya zurfafa rikicin siyasa da Ennahdha kan zarge-zargen da ake yi wa Fakhfakh na rikice-rikicen sha'awa.
Dangantaka tsakanin shugaban mai barin gado da Ennahdha mai shekaru 47 ta tabarbare tun bayan zaben majalisar dokoki na Oktoba.
Fakhfakh ya sauka a wannan rana da jam'iyyar ta gabatar da kudirin rashin amincewa da shi.
Da farko Ennahdha ya zabi wani mai zaman kansa na Firayim Minista, amma ya kasa samun goyon bayan majalisar, lamarin da ya sa shugaban kasar ya nada tsohon Ministan Kudi Fakhfakh a mukamin.
Da yake fuskantar yiwuwar sake gudanar da sabon zabe, Ennahdha daga karshe ya amince ya shiga gwamnatin hadin gwiwa.
Mota ta wuce cikin jama'a, an harbi mai zanga-zanga a cikin Colorado
Aurora, Colo. (AP)-Mota ta bi ta cikin jama'a kuma an harbe wani mai zanga-zanga a cikin garin Denver na kewayen Aurora yayin zanga-zangar adawa da rashin adalcin launin fata.
Ofishin "yan sanda na Aurora ya fada a shafin Twitter cewa masu zanga-zangar suna tafiya ne a kan babbar hanyar ta 225 ranar Asabar lokacin da abin hawa ya wuce.
'Yan sanda sun ce wani mai zanga-zangar ya harba makami, ya buge akalla mutum daya da aka kai shi asibiti cikin kwanciyar hankali.
Hukumomi sun ce an ja motar kuma suna ci gaba da bincike.
"Yan sanda sun ce masu zanga-zangar sun kuma fasa tagogi a harabar kotun kuma an fara wuta a wani ofishi.
An bayyana taron haramtacce kuma 'yan sanda sun umarci masu zanga-zangar su bar yankin, in ji hukumomi.
Tashin hankali ya ta'azzara a zanga-zangar baya-bayan nan game da rashin adalcin launin fata tun lokacin da aka tura jami'an gwamnatin tarayya don dakatar da zanga-zanga a Portland, Oregon.
'Yan sanda sun ayyana tarzoma a Seattle ranar Asabar.
Zanga-zangar da aka yi sakamakon mutuwar 25 ga watan Mayu na George Floyd, wani bakar fata a Minnesota wanda ya mutu bayan da wani jami'in farar fata ya rike shi a kasa tare da gwiwa zuwa wuyansa, sun kuma nuna wasu batutuwa na tashin hankalin "yan sanda.
A cikin Colorado, masu zanga-zangar sun ja hankali game da mutuwar Elijah McClain, wanda 'yan sanda suka tsayar yayin da yake tafiya a kan titin Aurora a watan Agusta 2019 bayan mai kiran 911 ya ba shi rahoton cewa yana tuhuma.
'Yan sanda sun sanya shi a cikin wani shinge, kuma masu ba da agajin gaggawa sun ba da miligram 500 na ketamine, mai kwantar da hankali, don kwantar da hankalinsa.
Ya shiga cikin kamawar zuciya, daga baya aka bayyana shi kwakwalwa ya mutu kuma ya cire tallafin rai.
Famously bayyana Lake Tahoe an ƙazantar da canjin yanayi
Kudancin Lake Tahoe, California-Duk da cutar, ko da a ranar mako, mutane har yanzu suna taron Paparoma Beach a Lake tahoe.
Wata yarinya mai suna Dakota ta ce "Ina son yin zango da tuka keke da zuwa iyo a Tekun".
"Wannan wani abu ne mai kyau da kowa ke so ya ziyarta", in ji Emerica Benitas.
Abin da ya sa har ila yau kasuwancin Matt Meunier ke ci gaba da ƙarfi, har ma a cikin annoba.
Ya ce yana ganin "tsabtar tsabta. Tabkin Tahoe shi ne mafi tsafta, mafi ban mamaki tafki, a ganina, a ƙasar".
Yanzu labari mara dadi: Tabkin Tahoe bashi da tsafta, ba mai haske bane, kamar yadda yake a lokacin da ya koma nan sama da shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
Meunier ya ce "Abubuwan da muke lura da su da yawa suna kan duwatsu",
"Kuna samun wannan algae mai ban mamaki a kan kankara".
Canjin yanayi, masana kimiyya sunyi imani, ya shafi zafin ruwan kuma don haka, tsabta.
Kuma mutane miliyan 15 suna ziyartar tafkin duk shekara-tare da shara da suke barinwa.
Meunier ya ce tafiye-tafiyen nutsewa don tsaftace ƙasan tafkin da aka samo tsofaffin shara.
Meunier ya ce "Kuma idan na ce tsohon shara, ina nufin '60s, 70s,'
"Gwangwani na giya, gwangwanin soda, gwangwani masu mahimmanci na coci daga tsohuwar kwanakin".
Masana kimiyya suna lura da bayyane tafkin Tahoe kowace shekara ta hanyar sauke farin diski, sa'annan su auna yadda zasu iya ganinta.
Farfesan UC Davis, Geoff Schladow, ya ce "muhimmiyar manuniya ce ta yadda lafiyayyar take da lafiya."
Lokacin da aka auna shi a bara, bayyananniyar tabkin yakai ƙafa 80.
Wannan yana nufin za ku iya ganin faifan 80 ƙafa ƙasa.
Amma, la'akari da wannan, kimanin shekaru 20 da suka gabata, bayyananniyar tabki yakai ƙafa 100.
Wannan shine yanayin da masana kimiyya ke ƙoƙarin juyawa.
Amma suna yaki da tasirin canjin yanayi, ci gaba a kusa da tafkin da wani abu da aka kara wa tabkin a shekarun 1960: Wani karamin tsiro mai cin zali da aka kawo don ciyar da kifin.
Bai yi aiki ba.
"Da zarar shrimp ta shigo, ba zato ba tsammani babu masu tsabtace yanayi a cikin tafkin", in ji Schladow.
Irin wannan kalubalen na fuskantar tabkuna da jikkunan ruwa a duniya.
"Darasin da ke nan shi ne, idan ba za ka iya yi a Tahoe ba, to mene ne fata ga dukkan koguna da wuraren hawan kawara, koguna da tafkuna a kewayen ƙasar waɗanda ba za su taɓa samun digiri iri ɗaya ba, irin matakin albarkatu?" Schladow ya ce.
Meunier ya ce yana da "fata" saboda "idan akwai rufin azurfa na annobar mu, ina ganin hakan ya nuna cewa yanayi zai dawo ya warkar da kansa idan har kawai mun sauƙaƙe wannan matsin lamba, na matsin lamba na mutum, daga gare shi kuma muka ƙyale hakan ta faru. Akwai hujjoji a can yanzu".
