Scotland-England Union Chain Bridge tana da shekaru 200
Wata gada da ta hada Scotland da Ingila ta cika shekaru 200 kafin a gyara fan miliyan 10.
Gadar Union Chain ta tsallaka Kogin Tweed daga Fishwick a cikin Yankin Scotland zuwa Horncliffe a Northumberland.
Lokacin da aka buɗe shi a 1820, ita ce gada mafi tsayi da aka dakatar da baƙin ƙarfe a duniya tare da tsayin 449ft (137m).
Shi ne kuma na farko vehicular gada na da irin a Birtaniya.
Jami'in sojan ruwa na kasar Ingila Capt Samuel Brown ne ya tsara gadar.
Ya mallaki kamfani kuma ya samar da sarƙoƙin ƙarfe bayan asarar jiragen ruwa na Royal Naval waɗanda suka yanke daga igiyoyi ya shafa shi.
Abokai na Union Chain Bridge da kuma Institution of Civil Engineers (Ice) Scotland an sa alama da mararraba ta bicentennial.
Robert Hunter, na kungiyar abokai, ya ce: "Hakika wannan daya ne daga cikin gadoji masu tarihi a duniya kuma wani yanki ne mai ban sha'awa na aikin injiniya.
"Mun shirya wasu bukukuwa da dama domin murnar wannan ranar, amma abin takaici dole ne a dage su.
"Duk da haka, gaskiyar cewa za a fara aiki nan ba da jimawa ba kan gyaran £10m shine mafi kyaun ranar haihuwar da za a yi kuma zai tabbatar da tsararraki masu zuwa za su iya jin daɗin gadar a duk ƙawarta".
Ice Scotland darektan Hannah Smith ya bayyana gada a matsayin "sau da yawa-saba shukawa" wani ɓangare na Scotland ta aikin injiniya al'adunmu.
Ta ce: "Mun san sanannen duniya ne kuma yana da kyau cewa ba da daɗewa ba za a fara aikin sabunta shi".
Barkewar cutar Salmonella ta cutar da mutane 212 a cikin jihohi 23
25 ga Yuli (UPI)-Cibiyoyin Kula da Rigakafin Cututtuka suna binciken barkewar cutar salmonella wacce ta yi wa mutane 212 rashin lafiya a cikin jihohi 23 na kasar.
A wata sanarwa da aka fitar a ranar Juma'a CDC ta ruwaito cewa mutane 87 sun kamu da rashin lafiya tun bayan sabuntawar da ta yi game da barkewar cutar a ranar Talata.
Hukumar ta ce mutane sun fara nuna alamun da ke da nasaba da nau'in salmonella, wanda zai iya daukar makonni biyu zuwa hudu don bayyana alamun cutar, tsakanin 19 ga Yuni da 11 ga Yuli.
An kwantar da mutane talatin da daya a asibiti tun lokacin da cutar ta fara, amma ba a samu rahoton mutuwa ba.
A cewar CDC, ba a gano takamaiman tushe don cutar salmonella ba.
Ba ta bayar da wata sanarwa ba game da cin ko cinye wasu abinci na musamman, ba kuma masu sayar da kayayyaki masu suna waɗanda ke iya siyar da gurbataccen kayayyaki ba.
Oregon ya sami mafi yawan lokuta na salmonella, tare da cututtuka 51, tare da'Utah yana biye da baya tare da rahoton rahoton 40.
Salmonella cuta ce ta kwayar cuta, cututtukan abinci da ke haifar da cututtuka miliyan 1.35, kwantar da asibiti 26,500, da kuma mutuwar 420 kowace shekara, a cewar CDC.
Mafi yawan alamun cututtukan salmonella sune gudawa, zazzabi, da ciwon ciki, wanda zai iya farawa tsakanin sa'o'i shida da kwanaki shida bayan fallasa.
Rashin lafiya yawanci yakan ɗauki kwanaki huɗu zuwa bakwai, kuma yawancin mutane suna warkewa ba tare da magani ba, amma wasu lokuta suna buƙatar asibiti.
United, Chelsea cikin CL; Bournemouth, Watford daga EPL
Manchester United da Chelsea sun tsallake zuwa gasar zakarun Turai tare da Leicester a ranar karshe ta kakar Premier ta bana a ranar Lahadi, yayin da Bournemouth da Watford suka fice don kawo karshen zaman shekaru biyar a saman jirgi.
United ta ci 2-0 a Leicester ta hannun kwallayen da Bruno Fernandes da Jesse Lingard suka zira mata don bai wa kungiyar Ole Gunnar Solskjaer damar kammalawa a matsayi na uku.
Chelsea ta doke Wolverhampton da ci 2-0 bayan kwallo daya da kuma taimakawa daga Mason Mount kuma ta kare a matsayi na hudu kuma na karshe na cancantar shiga gasar zakarun Turai sama da Leicester, wacce ta kasance cikin manyan kungiyoyi hudu a tsawon kakar.
Leicester, a maimakon haka, za ta buga gasar cin kofin Europa tare da Tottenham, wanda ya tashi kunnen doki 1-1 a Crystal Palace don tabbatar da matsayi na shida-sama da Wolverhampton da bambancin kwallaye.
Yakin don kauce wa sauran ragowar rukunin faduwa biyu ya tafi ne a waya yayin da Aston Villa ta ci kwallo a minti na 84, aka zira minti daya daga baya, sannan aka ci gaba da yin kunnen doki 1-1 a West Ham don tsira.
Kyaftin Jack Grealish ne ya ci wa Villa kwallon da za ta iya zama wasan karshe da zai yi wa kulob dinsa na boyhood.
Bournemouth ta yi abin da ta kamata kuma ta doke Everton, da ci 3-1, amma ta kare da maki daya a bayan Villa.
Ita ma Watford ta fice daga wasan gaba-da-karshe bayan ta sha kashi a hannun Arsenal da ci 3-2.
Manchester City ta ci kwallaye 100 don kamfen din ta da ci 5-0 a kan karshe da kuma riga-kafi da Norwich, wasan da ya nuna shi ne na karshe a Premier na David Silva bayan shekaru 10 tare da City.
Kevin De Bruyne ya sami nasarar buga rikodin na 20 na kakar kuma ya ci kwallaye biyu.
Liverpool ta kammala gasar cin kofin ta bana da ci 3-1 a hannun Newcastle kuma ta kare da maki 99 a kulob din.
Haka kuma, Southampton ta doke Sheffield United da ci 3-1, inda Danny Ings ya ci kwallonsa ta 22 a bana.
Hakan ya sa ya zama na daya a bayan Jamie Vardy na Leicester, wanda ya ci Kofin Zinare a matsayin wanda ya fi kowa zira kwallaye a gasar.
Tony Blair ya yi alwashin ba zai daina tsoma baki a cikin siyasar Birtaniya ba duk da tsananin raunin Brexit
Tony Blair ya yi alƙawarin ba zai daina tsoma baki a cikin siyasar Burtaniya ba, biyo bayan mummunan martani da aka samu game da sa hannu a cikin Jam'iyyar Labour da kamfen ɗin adawa da Brexit.
Mista Blair, wanda ya kwashe sama da shekaru goma ba ya aiki, ya shaida wa Sophy Ridge a Sky News cewa "ba zai" daina daina magana ba a siyasar Burtaniya.
Duk da haka, da rigima siyasa adadi yarda "mai yawa mutane kallon wannan zai iya tunanin ya kamata in daina magana game da abubuwa".
Sophy Ridge ya gaya wa Mista Blair: "A koyaushe ina jin cewa ba za ka iya nisantar da kanka daga siyasa ba".
"Kullum kuna wallafa rahotanni a kan coronavirus ko kuma ku fito da muhawara a kan Brexit".
"Ina kawai mamaki idan mutane suna tunani, me yasa bayan shekaru goma da zama PM, har yanzu kuna kokarin shiga siyasa?"
"Shin lokaci bai yi ba da za a ɗan ɗan daɗe, a zaga filin wasan golf".
Tsohon Firayim Ministan ya yi watsi da wannan kuma ya sha alwashin ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin siyasar Burtaniya muddin zai iya.
Ya ce: "Ba abu ne da nake so in yi ba. Yawancin mutane da ke kallon na iya tunanin hakan shi ne ainihin abin da ya kamata ya yi kuma ya daina magana game da abubuwa, amma na damu da kasar".
"Muna cikin wani babban lokaci na canji a duniya kuma cibiyar da na gina ayyuka a duniya".
"Na san na yi wani abu da Firayim ministocin da suka gabata ba su yi ba amma a nan gaba ina hasashen da yawa da za su yi kokarin yi".
Tun da farko a cikin tattaunawar, Mista Blair ya ce har yanzu Birtaniya da EU na iya kulla yarjejeniya a kan Brexit kafin karshen shekarar.
Ya ce: "Za su iya kulla yarjejeniya. Amma ko da yarjejeniyar da za mu kulla za ta kasance mara kyau".
"Da gaske ne zai kasance mai kyau ga Turai saboda zai ba da damar sauƙin cinikayya a cikin kayayyaki amma yana hana mu sosai a kan batun ayyuka".
Tsohon shugaban na Labour din ya kuma fada wa Sky News cewa Burtaniya za ta kasance tare da COVID-19, ba kawar da ita ba, nan gaba.
A Lokacin Jinjinawa Ga jarumai na Kargil, Firayim Minista Narendra Modi ya ce Pakistan ta yi kokarin "Backstab" Indiya
Pakistan ta yi kokarin "dawo da martabar" Indiya duk da kokarin da ta yi na ci gaba da huldar abokantaka, Firayim Minista Narendra Modi ya fada yau a cikin gudunmuwa da ya bayar ga sojojin kasar a bikin cika shekaru 21 da yakin Kargil.
A cikin jawabin sa na wata na rediyo mai suna Mann ki baat, Firayim Minista Modi ya ce "Pakistan ta gudanar da wannan mummunan aiki tare da munanan shirye-shirye na kwace kasar ta Indiya da kuma juya akalar rikice-rikicen cikin ta".
"Pakistan na da karfin gwiwa na kokarin mamaye kasar Indiya tare da karkatar da hankali daga tashin hankalin da ake ciki", in ji shi.
"A lokacin, Indiya na ƙoƙarin inganta dangantaka da Pakistan. Amma kamar yadda aka ce, muguwar dabi'a ita ce yaƙi da kowa ba tare da dalili ba. Mutanen da ke da irin wannan dabi'a za su iya tunanin aikata mugunta kawai ga waɗanda ke ƙoƙarin yi musu alheri. Me ya sa Pakistan ta tsaya wa Indiya baya duk da ƙoƙarin da Indiya ke yi na kulla kyakkyawar alaka," in ji shi..
Ya kara da cewa "Kuna iya tunanin, abokan gaba sun kasance a tsaunuka yayin da sojojinmu ke yakarsu daga kasa. Amma babban halin kirki da na gaskiya na sojojinmu ya yi nasara akan tsaunuka", in ji shi.
"Saboda karfin gwiwar da sojojinmu suka nuna, Indiya ta nuna matukar karfi a Kargil", in ji PM Modi, yana mai tuno ziyarar da ya kai yankin.
Ana yin bikin Kargil Diwas a kowace shekara, wanda ke nuna ranar da Sojojin Indiya suka sake kwato dukkan sakonnin Indiya a cikin Kargil na Ladakh da sojojin Pakistan suka mamaye shekaru 21 da suka gabata.
A ranar 26 ga Yuli, 1999, Sojojin sun ba da sanarwar nasarar nasarar "Operation Vijay".
Yakin da aka kwashe kusan watanni uku ana yi a tsaunukan da ake yin sanyi a garin Ladakh ya salwantar da rayukan sojojin Indiya sama da 500.
Tun da farko a yau, ministan tsaro Rajnath Singh, karamin ministansa Shripad Naik, Babban hafsan hafsoshi Janar Bipin Rawat, shugaban sojoji Janar M Naravane, Air Chief Marshal RK S Bhadauria da Chief Navy Chief Admiral Karambir Singh suma sun yi yabo a Amar Jawan Jyoti a National Memorial War.
A cikin shekarun da suka gabata tun daga Kargil, dangantakar Indiya da Pakistan ta tabarbare sakamakon jerin hare-haren ta'addanci.
Indiya ta dage kan cewa tattaunawa da ta'addanci ba za su iya tafiya kafada da kafada ba kuma Pakistan na bukatar tarwatsa dukkan sansanonin ta'addancin da ke aiki daga kasarta.
Gwyneth Paltrow na son yara su kasance da 'kyawawan dabi'u'
